text: Your Corporate Export application has been approved, and you can now <https://ipsentinel.slack.com/services/export|perform Corporate Exports> for your workspace.

At the moment, anyone in your workspace can invite a new member. If you like, you can restrict that to just administrators.
<slack-action://BSLACKBOT/users-invites/invites-only-admins/restrict/|Only allow administrators to invite>

At the moment anyone in your workspace can invite a new member. If you like, you can change that so invitations require admin approval. To turn it on, head over to the *<https://my.slack.com/admin/settings#invites|settings & permission page>*.
You’ve upgraded your Slack workspace :tada:. Now’s a good time to make sure your whole team is here.
